      "rating": 5,
      "text": "Nyummy food and cool place i like it >:3 i hope theres a pudding",
      "textTranslated": "Makanannya enak dan tempatnya keren, aku suka >:3 kuharap ada pudingnya",
      "date": "2026-01-14T02:59:55.984Z",
      "relativeDate": "3 bulan lalu",
      "likesCount": 0,
      "responseFromOwner": "Dear Guest,\n\nWarmest Greetings from ARYADUTA BANDUNG\n\nThank you for sharing your wonderful review. We are delighted to know that you enjoyed the yummy food and loved the ambiance of our place. Your kind words truly mean a lot to us and motivate our team to keep delivering memorable experiences.\n\nWe also appreciate your sweet suggestion about having pudding on the menu. We will certainly share this with our culinary team as we continuously strive to enhance our offerings and provide more delightful options for our guests.\n\nWe look forward to welcoming you back soon for another enjoyable dining experience at ARYADUTA Bandung.\n\nRegards,\n\nManagement\nARYADUTA Bandung",
